user_query: I'm organizing a charity event and I want to include some humorous elements. Can you suggest some funny jokes and quotes to use in the event program? Also, find me some interesting manatee jokes and random Chuck Norris jokes to entertain the attendees.

TaskList.description: Gather a collection of general funny jokes and quotes suitable for a charity event.
Search for specific manatee jokes to include in the event program.
Find random Chuck Norris jokes for entertainment purposes.
Compile all jokes and quotes into a formatted document for the event program.
